metadata.name: Dandelions
metadata.description:
1/1
mp4, 1920 x 1080, 21sec
music by Arash Ashayeri

Absolute blackness
Dream creation

We are all born and live in a black hole, and we may return to a deeper black hole in another world.
Maybe death, like the death of dandelion feathers, separates us from our being and flies away
Nobody knows
